  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA19">
<l>iṉṟu namakkeḷitē mālukku nāṉmukaṟku</l>
<l>maṉṟu maḷappariya ṉāṉāṉai - yeṉṟumōr</l>
<l>mūvā matiyāṉai mūvē ḻulakaṅka</l>
<l>ḷāvāṉaik kāṇu maṟivu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Today it is easy for us – the knowledge that sees him</l>
<l>who had become difficult to measure that day for Māl and the four-faced one,</l>
<l>the one always with an unaging moon,</l>
<l>the one who is the thrice seven worlds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
